data.description: Hard to find, well-maintained ranch style home in the Heart of Weston, 3Bed/2Bath, new 17 SEER HVAC / Air Scrubber for pollution, cleaned air ducts, new ECO system water heater. Recently painted interior/exterior/garage. Steel appliances, with new microwave. Upgraded kitchen with granite.  All rooms have ceiling fans. Hurricane Shutters. Reinforced closets can hold 2X more.    Gated Community, safe neighborhood 24/7 Private Security. Heated swimming pools, for prof. and rec. use. Soccer fields, mini golf, coffee shop. Low HOA fees, and buyer doesn't need HOA approval. No restriction for pets. Quite neighborhood. Easy Show.  All School rated are A+. Close to Saw Grass Mall.
